                "html": "While most treasure a roc may possess is incidental\u2014the remains of prey haphazardly scattered in or around the nest\u2014roc feathers, especially white or gold ones, are highly prized in certain markets. Even more valuable are roc eggs, especially to some giants who enjoy their unique flavor."
